  "title": "Senior Draughtsperson",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>· Prepare and submit standard drawing & as-built drawings in accordance to project requirement;</p><p>· Maintain all drawing files, update drawings as needed, and make corrections to drawing as needed; good work housekeeping/ organizing;</p><p>· Prepare the drawing and document set for authorities submission;</p><p>· Support in tender if required;</p><p>· Perform on site measurement and site survey;</p><p>· Able to undertake any other duties as assigned;<br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong><br /></p><p>· Minimum Diploma in C&S Engineering or equivalent.</p><p>· At least 4 years of relevant working experience.</p><p>· Able to multi-task, work independently, proactive with positive attitude.</p><p>· Good knowledge of Autodesk cad software and BIM software / tools. (Autodesk Revit & Tekla).</p><p>· Proficient in MS Office. (Words, Excel and PowerPoint)</p>",
